org.jboss.soa.esb.visitors
Class ServiceDelegator

java.lang.Object
  org.jboss.soa.esb.visitors.ServiceDelegator
Deprecated. Use FragmentRouter 

public class ServiceDelegator
extends java.lang.Object

ServiceDelegateVisitor is a Smooks visitor that delegates to a JBoss ESB service.

Sample config (smooks-res.xml) : 

  <param name="service-category-name">FirstServiceESB</param>
  <param name="service-name">sendToJMSQueue</param>
This class is intended to be used as a delegator for Smooks Visitors, like a DOMVisitor or a SAXVisitor.

Author:
Daniel Bevenius
